HEADWORD: Wafture
<hw>Waf"ture</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of waving; a
wavelike motion; a waft.</def> <rj><au>R. Browning.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

